The R code is supplementary to the publication \'84\cf0 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Agricultural land use alters temporal dynamics and the composition of organic matter in temperate headwater streams\'93 and was used to calculate generalized additive models (GAM) in the analysis of stream organic matter standing crops and to test whether temporal patterns in response variables were significantly different between landuse types. \
